{"tid":1334492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非遊行人士注意]聽日遊行須知","createTime":"2019-07-20T06:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:10:26.000Z","uid":42149,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"334d06b8ed778c0e77fb0451425a49166437171e","tid":1334492,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"麻煩遊行人士，一齊戴上頭盔，如果可以既話戴埋口罩<br />\n以行動方式同警察示威，抗議警方用暴力對待遊行人士及令社會動盪不安。<br />\n而且你頭上個頂頭盔可供其他有須要人士使用。<br />\n及<br />\n可保護有須要人士。不論前線或遊行人士，我地坐係同一條船，要互相協作<br />\n所以懇請各和理非遊行人士。戴上頭盔，口罩遊行"},{"pid":"531c1b3fee54b4f078e934798106282a41db2521","tid":1334492,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:29:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[沙盤推演] 大家有無諗過呢場抗爭既end game係點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1334346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1334346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e368c31ae50e5d6ef09df4070248e9983bc7d8f","tid":1334492,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6330699590b274a0fbbd0b209401abf93246ed7f","tid":1334492,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fefb5df2469b0e27ce7a51ab3d2ef143595c965","tid":1334492,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"1. 保護義士<br />\n越多人戴口罩，義士越安全。上禮拜沙田，其實好多狗都係針對戴左口罩嘅人。只要大家都戴口罩，就有機會減低犬方對義士落手嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.對付愛港人士<br />\n有傳政府內部AO話政府將喺721出大量不名人士，主動同示威者起衝突，以製造混亂，耗損我方兵力<br />\n<br />\n雖然好難保證真定假，但最好應該避免咗先<br />\n<br />\n唔排除現場一定會有大量鬼，收咗錢影相，所以為咗保護自己同身邊嘅人，叫佢哋一定要戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺我多次發夢，上禮拜上水同之前屯門，或再之前者之金鐘，都係有人影相，先會起衝突。<br />\n<br />\n如果政府想出一班人主動起衝突，好難嚟唔開用影人相，所以就算大家係和理非，都唔該戴咗口罩先，以減少佢哋落手嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預防瘋狗症，記得帶口罩"},{"pid":"fc0d8ecee70e5770579640e6a3fb24700512247f","tid":1334492,"uid":210612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d29824cd3018e69833d7d3fedb18f99e7f8bbd","tid":1334492,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f46faab8b8e761c4aa56f8cc999628d998ba71c9","tid":1334492,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc0d8ecee70e5770579640e6a3fb24700512247f","tid":1334492,"uid":210612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"落場帶， 出門口帶好易比狗逗"},{"pid":"28bd048f4ebbb889caa1e8c06668e5f102e7b0dd","tid":1334492,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95b193b8501a0317c9670832eccee4d50f0952ec","tid":1334492,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:16:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"072c52643352550df5092a5151828fbeb2edabfa","tid":1334492,"uid":52701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"無頭盔但都照行支持你地！"}]}